txt.en: 'In the far reaches of southern Mirkwood, the fortress of Dol Guldur stands atop a rocky height. It was the stronghold of the Enemy for a time, and still his evil festers there.\n\n'I walked there once, long ago. The memory is grim, and were it not for my companion on that journey I would have despaired. If all goes well, we will not need to tread where I once did, and for that I am grateful.'
What do we know about Dol Guldur?
